OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779390672
OL,3,CTop Israeli diplomat in UK summoned
OL,4,Cover 'inflammatory' video of detainees
OL,6,FThe UK has summoned Israel's most
OL,7,Fsenior diplomat in Britain over an
OL,8,F"inflammatory" video of detainees
OL,9,Fposted by the country's security
OL,10,Fminister.
OL,12,FIsraeli minister Itamar Ben-Gvir drew
OL,13,Finternational condemnation after
OL,14,Fsharing footage taunting international
OL,15,Factivists detained in Israel following
OL,16,Ftheir attempt to break the country's
OL,17,Fblockade of Gaza on an aid flotilla.
OL,19,FIsrael's charge d'affaires Daniela
OL,20,FGrudsky Ekstein was summoned to the
OL,21,FForeign Office on Thursday.
OL,26,@{D@Orr
