PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779390672
OL,3,CTop Israeli diplomat in UK summoned
OL,4,Cover 'inflammatory' video of detainees
OL,6,FThe UK said the move reflected its
OL,7,F"strong condemnation" of Ben-Gvir's
OL,8,Fbehaviour in taunting those involved
OL,9,Fin the Global Sumud Flotilla.
OL,11,F"This behaviour violates the most
OL,12,Fbasic standards of respect and dignity
OL,13,Ffor people," the department said.
OL,15,FGrudsky Ekstein is the most senior
OL,16,FIsraeli diplomat in the UK, as there
OL,17,Fis currently no ambassador in place.
OL,26,@sD@AOUuD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
