PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779390672
OL,3,CTop Israeli diplomat in UK summoned
OL,4,Cover 'inflammatory' video of detainees
OL,6,FThe government also expressed concern
OL,7,Fover the detention conditions shown in
OL,8,Fwhat appeared to be a makeshift
OL,9,Fholding area in Ashdod, on Israel's
OL,10,Fcoast, and demanded an explanation
OL,11,Ffrom Israeli authorities.
OL,13,FThe Foreign Office said it is in touch
OL,14,Fwith the families of a number of
OL,15,FBritish activists detained in Israel
OL,16,Fand is ready to provide consular
OL,17,Fsupport.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
