OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779390672
OL,3,CTop Israeli diplomat in UK summoned
OL,4,Cover 'inflammatory' video of detainees
OL,6,FMore than 400 people have been
OL,7,Fdetained following the attempt,
OL,8,Fincluding several British nationals
OL,9,Fand Catherine Connolly, the sister of
OL,10,Fthe Irish president.
OL,12,FA similar bid by activists in 2025
OL,13,Falso ended with Israel intercepting
OL,14,Fthe vessels and detaining those on
OL,15,Fboard.
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
