PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779390672
OL,3,CTop Israeli diplomat in UK summoned
OL,4,Cover 'inflammatory' video of detainees
OL,6,FForeign Secretary Yvette Cooper said
OL,7,FWednesday she was "truly appalled" by
OL,8,Fthe footage released by Ben-Gvir,
OL,9,Fwhich showed some activists with their
OL,10,Fhands tied behind their backs and
OL,11,Fkneeling with their heads touching the
OL,12,Ffloor.
OL,14,FThe videos were also criticised by
OL,15,FIsraeli Prime Minister Benjamin
OL,16,FNetanyahu, who said it was "not in
OL,17,Fline with Israel's values and norms".
