OL,3,CTop Israeli diplomat in UK summoned
OL,4,Cover 'inflammatory' video of detainees
OL,6,FThe UK sanctioned Ben-Gvir and his
OL,7,Ffellow minister Bezalel Smotrich in
OL,8,FJune 2025, over the two's "repeated
OL,9,Fincitement of violence against
OL,10,FPalestinian civilians".
